his in my line of work. I am sure Willaen (OOC: Kelethin Banker) has, knowing what that fellow has to put up with. However my advice to you is that you look try some of your guildmates. Thats what alot of people that are overstocked usually do.&quot;<br><br>   Vanyarian rubbed his chin. &quot;That's a good idea. I will send word to Halas immediately.&quot; With that he turned and hurried out of the bank, leaving the beleagured banker to try and shut the vault.<br><br>&lt;sitting down in his study he begins to write a letter&gt;<br>   Hail Maclear! I have a rather...abundant stockpile of equipment in my vault and on me. There is nothing truly &quot;amazing&quot; per say, but most of it is useful. I ask anyone interested in...well just about anything to send me a tell. Do not ask for anything amazing, but if ye need something (especially good druid or cleric equipment, or banded armor) feel free to ask and MAYBE I can provide it. As is my custom I will give a bargain price. Alas, I cannot provide a full inventory, because I have to go check my fault again to see what is in it. Stay well brothers! For Halas! For Maclear!<br><br>-Vanyarian Singollo-Ranger of Tunare<br>&quot;All that is gold does not glitter, All that wander are not lost&quot;<br><br>&lt;after a flipping a plat to a lad to have the letter sent, he runs down the street to go take an inventory&gt;<br>  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm5.showPrevMessage?topicID=35.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm5.showNextMessage?topicID=35.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=35.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95